snippet.title: CAMDEA Digital Forum
snippet.description:
Welcome to the CAMDEA Digital Forum youtube channel.
We host free, online/ digital, tech events every month dedicated to the Artificial Intelligence, Machine Learning, Data Science, Engineering & Analytics Industries across Canada.

We don't charge people to attend our events and NEVER will. 
You can explore our community and upcoming events here: 
https://www.meetup.com/CAMDEA-Digital-Forum/
